description: Attention Investors and Developers! Spacious three-family property located on the east side of South Boston. 3 three-bedroom units. 3,579 sq/ft of living area in total.  Large rooms with open floor plan. The first floor unit has been expanded to the lower level (Duplex style) with tall ceilings and walkout to a spacious backyard. Patio in back yard is great space fpr summer BBQ's.  Large private decks off the back of each unit.  Laundry hook up in each unit.  Great condo conversion or investment opportunity in an area poised for continued growth with lots of new development and popular with young professionals. Ideally located between L & K Street, just two blocks from the beach, a short walk to East Broadway with all of Southie's trendy restaurants, and in close proximity to Seaport. Property to be delivered vacant. The property is being sold "AS IS" with no warranties or representations from Sellers or Brokers.  Do not miss this opportunity to own in a prime location in South Boston.
